###
# Social Media Integration API Tests
###

### Get available platforms (no auth required)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/social/platforms

### Mock connect Instagram (requires JWT token)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/social/mock-connect/instagram
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

### Get connected accounts (requires JWT token)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/social/accounts
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

### Sync platform metrics (requires JWT token)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/social/accounts/instagram/sync
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

### Check connection status (requires JWT token)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/social/accounts/instagram/status
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

### Disconnect account (requires JWT token)
DELETE http://localhost:3001/api/social/accounts/instagram
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

### OAuth callback (requires JWT token)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/social/oauth/callback
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "platform": "instagram",
  "code": "mock_auth_code_12345",
  "state": "optional_state_param"
}